text:
Great ambiance. Ample parking for visitors (paid but reasonable).

Good play options for kids and family.
Separate kids play zone and excellent pool with all facilities.

Food is delicious.

Bowling experience is awesome. Make sure to choose the right number balls to fir ones fingers.

Open beach opposite to this place.

Overall fantastic place for family/friend gathering or corporate events.

Worst curry fish head ever! No meat at all. Only some bones and a few strand of cabbages and lady's fingers. $42!! And when I complained, the service staff told me it's expected that there is no meat on fish head! She thought I first time ate fish head! I told her it's a feedback and she ought to acknowledge and bring it up to the  management and the chef. Instead she chided me that if I wanted more meat I should order a large. I will never go back there. Horrible service. And horrible food.
cheap and not crowded w place if got bungalow u get discount which is so good
The chicken chop is amazing and the food pricing is affordable
